{"tid":2515973,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"連登仔幾時先捨得打Biontech，到時俾政府強制又得番科興唔好喊～","createTime":"2021-05-04T10:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T10:44:41.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b250a5dd8cb412d143eaa4c52a0d1e4f6aab4b79","tid":2515973,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"成日話唔好慣唔好慣，鬼唔撚知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持乜乜柒柒唔好打針唔裝APP，最多買外賣自己煮，放棄一切娛樂。但係照咁睇好快連出入街市都要show針卡，搭車又要掃Code，到時連最基本嘅返工放工都要打針，咁你係咪又會話最多唔返工唔食飯？<br />\n<br />\n依家大家只不過係唔燒到我個曡先唔理住，當連最基本野都要打針，你一係就反抗，一係就移民，否則到最後你都要選擇打針。打針係人都驚，但係你唔打連最基本嘅人身自由同生計都會受到影響，最多睇吓邊個癱左就當佢唔好彩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家政府一批一批咁的D人去打<br />\n好快仲未打既人就愈黎愈少，到時再強制你都無聲出<br />\n過多幾個月個個埸所都要打，公務員又隨時強制，8月又得返科興，到時你唔好後悔。一係你即時逃離HK，再唔係一係週街乞食，否則一定燒到你個曡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住鬧翻我轉頭「咁你打咗未啊柒頭」<br />\n我講嗰啲嘢冚巴冷都係好實際，呢個就係你哋而家要面對嘅現實環境，自己睇路行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da66b7418ca0f76240cf3bf2917ee9ece3f15419","tid":2515973,"uid":226296,"like":1,"di